@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Delivered
Delivered --> Created : process
Created --> Archived : submit
Archived --> Completed : update
Completed --> OnHold : reject
OnHold --> Pending : submit
OnHold --> Completed : revert
Pending --> [*]
@enduml